OL,3,CMan arrested after woman in 80s
OL,4,Cattacked with scissors
OL,6,FA woman in her 80s has been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after being stabbed with a
OL,8,Fpair of scissors in Chatham.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to The Chase
OL,11,F2.07pm on Saturday 14 March to reports
OL,12,Fof a woman being attacked outside a
OL,13,Fprivate property.
OL,15,FOfficers attended alongside
OL,16,Fparamedics, who treated the woman in
OL,17,Fher 80s for injuries consistent with
OL,18,Fstab wounds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
