PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773673868
OL,3,CMan arrested after woman in 80s
OL,4,Cattacked with scissors
OL,6,FShe was taken to a London hospital for
OL,7,Ffurther treatment. Her injuries are
OL,8,Fnot believed to be life changing or
OL,9,Fthreatening.
OL,11,FA man was also reportedly assaulted by
OL,12,Fthe suspect, who was unknown to the
OL,13,Fvictims, before officers located and
OL,14,Farrested him at 2.31pm.
OL,16,FOrlando Foster, 25, has been charged
OL,17,Fwith wounding with intent, causing
OL,18,Factual bodily harm and making threats
OL,19,Fwith a bladed weapon in public.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
