PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773673868
OL,3,CMan arrested after woman in 80s
OL,4,Cattacked with scissors
OL,6,FThe British national, of Jeffery
OL,7,FStreet, Gillingham, was remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody until his first appearance at
OL,9,FMedway Magistrates' Court on Monday 16
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FIn response to this incident,
OL,13,Fincreased patrols will be present in
OL,14,Fthe area.
OL,16,FEnquiries are continuing into the
OL,17,Fcircumstances, however it is believed
OL,18,Fto be an isolated incident.
